                  <Text layoutX="30.0" layoutY="296.0" strokeType="OUTSIDE" strokeWidth="0.0" text="This topic connects geometry to algebra and helps you solve problems involving rotation, wave patterns, and circular motion. You’ll also begin to understand how trigonometry fits into broader mathematical models used in navigation, astronomy, and physics." textAlignment="JUSTIFY" wrappingWidth="727.7760620117188">
